#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Crazy Labs"
msgstr "瘋狂實驗室"

#. ~ Description for Crazy Labs
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"A mod that adds lots of tough monsters to lab monster gen. Now labs are "
"endgame areas! Intended for players who find labs too easy or boring. "
"Inspired by Half-Life and the labs in Resident Evil 2."
msgstr ""
"此模組為實驗室怪物生成添加了大量強力怪物。現在實驗室是終局區域！專為那些覺得實驗室太簡單或無聊的玩家設計。靈感來自《半條命》和《生化危機2》中的實驗室。"

